des:
With the GENIUS Skill you can simply ask to Alexa to turn it on, off, control the light intensity or even change the light color. No need to go to the switch to adjust your light, just talk to your Alexa device.

After connecting your Alexa device to your wifi network, just follow a few simple steps:
(1) Download our GENIUS app from the Google Play or Apple Store;
(2) Register an account on our GENIUS app;
(3) You need to have some GENIUS smart devices on hand;
(4) Sync these devices into our GENIUS app and change the appropriate name for your devices that will be used in Skill GENIUS;
(5) Download the “Alexa” app from the Apple Store or Google Play;
(6) Configure the Alexa device with the “Alexa” app;
(7) Search for GENIUS Skill in the Skills category of the “Alexa” app;
(8) Click Activate GENIUS Skill, and you will be directed to the GENIUS app login page;
(9) Enter with your e-mail and password of the account created earlier in the GENIUS app and you will be redirected to the success page;
(10) Now all setup is complete. You can enjoy voice control on your lighting products like these:
"Alexa, turn on the light in the bedroom."
"Alexa, turn off the light in the room."
"Alexa, adjust the room light brightness to 40 percent."
"Alexa, turn up the brightness in the room."
"Alexa, turn the bedroom light down by 50 percent."
"Alexa, change the bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, make the room lights warmer."
